node.text: #PaidEggvertising Ommm… let (that’s a quality dad joke right there) me tell you about a tasty little treat I just discovered- @justcrackanegg has omelet rounds and they are so delicious! node.text: Tell me you like to party without telling me you like to party.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Lowe in Gun Barrel City, Texas. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: The guy listens to Luke Bryan once and now he’s huntin’, fishin’, and lovin’ everyday.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on August 02, 2021 tagging @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 1 person, baby, standing and indoor.

node.text: Sometimes I get emotional thinking that one day Mia will be all grown up and locked in her room because her daddy is the only man she will ever love.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 30, 2021 tagging @justcrackanegg. May be an image of 3 people, child and indoor.

node.text: #PaidEggvertising Every single morning, these filthy animals wake me up way too early and start demanding things from me. Needless to say, I don’t have much time to myself. Luckily for me, @justcrackanegg is here to help! Now I’m cookin’ up a delicious scramble in just over a minute which allows more time for me to plot ways to escape from this zoo I live in. #getouttahere

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 26, 2021 tagging @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 5 people, child, people standing and indoor.

node.text: I asked Catherine if I could give her a back rub one night and nine months later we had Samuel. Can’t believe she fell for the same trick 3 times.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 26, 2021 tagging @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 2 people, baby and people standing.

node.text: That whole Bachelor thing is finally paying dividends!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 22, 2021 tagging @travismathew, and @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: We met nearly nine years ago. Never did I think we would one day be here taking a picture in front of a restaurant after eating dinner.

node.text: I’m starting to think these kids don’t know how to play hide and seek.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 15, 2021 tagging @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 2 people, child, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: My boys both said they wanted hair like daddy today. As a dad, it makes me so proud to know my sons want to be like me and as a realist it makes me kinda sad knowing they’ll never quite measure up. But keep chasing your dreams little dudes, no matter how unrealistic they may be!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on July 14, 2021 tagging @travismathew. May be an image of 2 people, child, people standing, shorts and outdoors.

node.text: For years, I’ve seen guys who golf wear @travismathew. Since I’m not a golfer, I never checked it out. Well, now they’re making everyday wear for men and let me just say- it is so freakin’ comfy! Shirt, shorts, shoes- all @travismathew.
